### [`v8.4.0`](https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/releases/8.4.0)
[Compare Source](https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/compare/8.3.0...8.4.0)
<img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19343/39393137-a14441ba-4a8f-11e8-90f9-c31599b5380b.jpg" alt="Bludor family coat of arms" width="220" height="242" align="right" />

Autoprefixer 8.4 brings new control comment to ignore next line.

@&#8203;vostrik implemented the @&#8203;levin-du’s idea of having control comment to disable only next property/rule:

```css
.logo {
    /* autoprefixer: ignore next */
    user-select: none; /* ← ignored */
    mask: url(mask.jpg); /* ← will be prefixed */
}

/* autoprefixer: ignore next */
::placholder /* ← ignored */ {
    text-decoration-style: dotted; /* ← will be prefixed */
}
```

